## File usage in the app

### `welcome-family@2x.jpg`
- **Where:** Welcome splash screen (Screen 0) + Final CTA screen (Screen 4)
- **Why:** Brand bookends — the family photo opens and closes the welcome flow
- **Treatment:** Full-bleed background, slow Ken Burns zoom on splash, frosted glass card overlay on final CTA

### `welcome-horizon@2x.jpg`
- **Where:** Feature slides (Screens 1, 2, 3) — In the moment / Thinking partner / 12 books
- **Why:** Same atmosphere, no characters competing with feature content
- **Treatment:** Full-bleed background, frosted glass card at bottom holds the feature copy

### 1x variants (`welcome-family.jpg`, `welcome-horizon.jpg`)
- Fallbacks for low-DPI devices
- Expo automatically picks 1x or @2x based on `PixelRatio.get()`

